{"tid":1020643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"為情所困","createTime":"2019-02-13T17:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T17:49:27.000Z","uid":201975,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f84d6564c11e14b05360f917a458efdc3f2220","tid":1020643,"uid":201975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:29:50.000Z","msg":"這一生 為情所困<br />\n只為當初你的心太真<br />\n這一生 癡癡戀戀<br />\n只為一個無法實現的諾言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpfvgxH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpfvgxH.png&h=9ffd6334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老公真係好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唱歌又好聽 再加埋深情既眼神<br />\n直頭好似唱緊比我聽咁<br />\n今個情人節 我淨係想同你過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71d6154987e5e496cebea61ca9aa459f9177d7f","tid":1020643,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"e870916578843477364ffc232a86a464ab5df776","tid":1020643,"uid":201975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71d6154987e5e496cebea61ca9aa459f9177d7f","tid":1020643,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"我同我老公不嬲都好"},{"pid":"d1f7614fc0587bbdfbbce5250357e7be350e9b17","tid":1020643,"uid":201975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMnEUqA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMnEUqA.png&h=b7c64af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實呢個live我已經睇咗幾百次<br />\n不過睇幾多次都唔厭<br />\n覺得佢唱歌個陣個嘴仔寧舍好睇<br />\n好想咀落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}